        "value": "i2"
      },
      {
        "label": "<p class=\"choice_paragraph\">The charge <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"positive lowercase q\"><math alttext=\"positive lowercase q\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle displaystyle=\"true\"><mo>+</mo><mi>q</mi></mstyle></math></span></span> remains at the boundary between the top and middle plate.</p>",
        "value": "i3"
      },
      {
        "label": "<p class=\"choice_paragraph\">The net charge of the top plate <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"positive lowercase q\"><math alttext=\"positive lowercase q\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle displaystyle=\"true\"><mo>+</mo><mi>q</mi></mstyle></math></span></span> goes to the bottom surface of the middle plate.</p>",
